if ((gs_knob_type_m <> KNOB_STYLE_NONE) & bKnobNoneType) | (bKnob & not(bKnobNoneType)) then ! --- Knob hotspots --- if _act_gs_editableKnobs then add a/2 + gs_knobHorPos, 0, (gs_drawerHeights[m] - 0.005)/2 + gs_knobVerPos_m * (gs_drawerHeights[m] - 0.005)/4 if iCabIndex = 1 then

! --- Knob ---
